        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Michael S. Monie\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Michael S. Monie:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I had it for the first time today. It won\u2019t be the last. History in a glass: <a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Commandaria\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Commandaria - Wikipedia</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yup, Michael\u2026have had it 5-6 times. Not very common to find at retail. Very good stuff<br>\nat a fair price. A bit like a Malmsey Madeira. More people should be familiar with this wine.<br>\nTom</p>",
