      {
        "id": 3312989,
        "name": "Eric Sch",
        "username": "Eric_Sch",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/e19adc/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-01-08T19:34:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>When my parents moved out of their house a couple years ago I found a bottle of late 40s Commandaria that must have been my grandfather\u2019s. It hadn\u2019t really been stored properly so I wasn\u2019t expecting much. Took it to a tasting at my off site as a lark but everyone was stunned at the rich flavors and deep character. Not something I could drink a ton of but it was quite pleasing. Haven\u2019t had any since them but would happily drink more if I come across it.</p>",
